  "title": "Business Analyst",
  "description": "<p><p>Act as a <strong>Business Analyst</strong> supporting insurance sales, distribution, and policy servicing functions.</p></p><p><p>Work closely with <strong>agency and distribution teams</strong> to understand business processes and translate requirements into functional specifications.</p></p><p><p>Support <strong>agency compensation and commission processes</strong>, ensuring accuracy and alignment with business rules.</p></p><p><p>Analyze end-to-end insurance workflows, identify gaps, and recommend process improvements.</p></p><p><p>Operate as a <strong>self-managed individual contributor</strong>, independently driving requirements gathering and delivery.</p></p><p><p>Collaborate with stakeholders across business and technology to ensure timely and effective solution implementation.</p></p>",
